name: Jembatan Kuning Tukad Yeh Unda
address: Tukad Yeh Unda, GCRW+27X, Sidemen, Karangasem, Kabupaten Karangasem, Bali 80864, Indonesia
review 1: Went with the guide tracking through the fields in Sidemen. Local guide, passionate, and  with good knowledge of the local agricultural habits. This was one if the last visiting points. Recommended, take guide, he showed us hitdden paths that we never would be able to discover ourselves.
review 2:
the bridge is yellow and underneath there is a river, you can take a bath or just for relaxing, i tried to take a shower and to go down its really easy
Better bring bikini for shower if u here
review 3:
Great little spot for photos. Nice view of the river from either side when on the bridge.

We drove across the bridge (on our scooter) and did a little loop of Sidemen. Worth the drive for beautiful scenery.
review 4: Dope little yellow suspension bridge in Sidemen. Get in, take your pics, and move on. Locals use this for crossing over the river, please don't impede their progress.
review 5: Simple yellow local suspension bridge... Gateway to a lovely scenic loop for a scooter ride.
